  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dad left me in the car - is a short survival horror game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Eugena, who was left alone in the car by her dad, and she can not get out no matter what she does. The only thing she can do is to travel through the otherworldly places that resemble her memories. Eugena has to find the way out of this nightmarish loop and rescue her siblings who got trapped with her.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you must manage your parameters, fight creepy monsters, and discover the story of Eugena's family and why her dad left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bright characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intriguing plot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shooting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dad left me in the car - is a short survival horror game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Eugena, who was left alone in the car by her dad, and she can not get out no matter what she does. The only thing she can do is to travel through the otherworldly places that resemble her memories. Eugena has to find the way out of this nightmarish loop and rescue her siblings who got trapped with her.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you must manage your parameters, fight creepy monsters, and discover the story of Eugena's family and why her dad left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bright characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intriguing plot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shooting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
